OL,3,CJersey Ports want #60 million to turn
OL,4,Cderelict La Folie Inn into hotel
OL,6,FMarc Clayson, head of Ports Real
OL,7,FEstate, says: "We're looking for a
OL,8,Fdevelopment investor to build a hotel
OL,9,Fon the main site and then bring the
OL,10,Fhistoric buildings back to life and
OL,11,Fincorporate them sympathetically into
OL,12,Fthe hotel development.
OL,14,F"We have investors potentially lined
OL,15,Fup, interested in development. That
OL,16,Fneeds to go through a transparent
OL,17,Fprocurement process, which will run
OL,18,Fover the next few months.
