OL,3,CJersey Ports want #60 million to turn
OL,4,Cderelict La Folie Inn into hotel
OL,6,F"The current estimate of the cost is
OL,7,F#60 million but that could be a lot
OL,8,Fhigher depending on the standard."
OL,10,FPorts adds: "A market study has
OL,11,Fexplored the types of hospitality uses
OL,12,Fthat would thrive here and be
OL,13,Fcommercially viable.
OL,15,F"Early insights suggest the site could
OL,16,Faccommodate a hotel of meaningful
OL,17,Fscale, with the potential for around
OL,18,F125-150 guest rooms, depending on
OL,19,Fplanning and design."
