OL,3,CJersey Ports want #60 million to turn
OL,4,Cderelict La Folie Inn into hotel
OL,6,FThe development is part of the wider
OL,7,Fmaster plan, which seeks to transform
OL,8,Fthe harbours in St Helier.
OL,10,FTom Wright, from the maritime
OL,11,Fprogramme at Ports, adds: "It is a
OL,12,Freal opportunity that this site has to
OL,13,Fblend heritage with future opportunity.
OL,15,F"We have this challenge across all of
OL,16,Four estate, where we have cultural
OL,17,Fhistory to bring alive and reflect it
OL,18,Fin what we do."
