OL,3,CJersey Ports want #60 million to turn
OL,4,Cderelict La Folie Inn into hotel
OL,6,FTourism bosses also hope that the
OL,7,Fproposed redevelopment will make the
OL,8,Fquay area a standout destination to
OL,9,Fdraw in visitors.
OL,11,FLee Madden, President of Jersey's
OL,12,FChamber of Commerce, explains: "It's a
OL,13,Fhalfway point between town and Havre
OL,14,FDes Pas, so you're going to have
OL,15,Fretailers and shops benefit.
OL,17,F"We're also going to have a massive
OL,18,Fcapital project to build it so
OL,19,Fconstruction firms and suppliers are
OL,20,Fall going to benefit from this, it's a
OL,21,Fwin-win.
