OL,3,CJersey Ports want #60 million to turn
OL,4,Cderelict La Folie Inn into hotel
OL,6,F"I think one of the issues we've had
OL,7,Fover the last 20 years is because we
OL,8,Fdidn't have the right planning
OL,9,Fattitude, but the attitude is
OL,10,Fabsolutely right now."
OL,12,FThe hope is that the project will be
OL,13,Fcompleted by 2027, provided an
OL,14,Finvestor can be found and the planning
OL,15,Fprocess is efficient.
